{% comment %}
  ============================================================================
  SOLEIL STYLESHEETS SNIPPET
  ============================================================================
  
  Purpose: Load Soleil theme styles into Horizon theme
  Usage: Include this snippet in layout/theme.liquid head section
  
  Example:
  {% render 'soleil-stylesheets' %}
  
  Aquí puedes agregar nueva información al código sin romperlo.
  ============================================================================
{% endcomment %}

{% comment %} /* Start Soleil + Custom Sections Stylesheets */ {% endcomment %}

{% comment %}
/* Start: Soleil Theme Styles */
  Loads the Soleil Beauty design system CSS:
  - CSS custom properties (colors, spacing, typography, shadows, radius)
  - Global typography (Inter + Playfair Display font stack)
  - Button, card, form, cart, footer base styles
/* End: Soleil Theme Styles */
{% endcomment %}
{{ 'soleil-theme.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}

{% comment %}
/* Start: Custom Sections CSS */
  Loads styles for:
  - Hero Banner Responsive (Luna Hernández)
  - New Arrivals Section (Luna Hernández)
  - Multicolumn Info Section (Luna Hernández)
  - Animated Announcement Bar (Koelleza dual-direction marquee)
  - Sephora-style product card enhancements
  - Visual separation utilities
/* End: Custom Sections CSS */
/* You can paste future updates here without breaking anything */
{% endcomment %}
{{ 'custom-sections.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}

{% comment %}
/* Start: Custom Sections JS */
  Loads JavaScript for:
  - New Arrivals carousel navigation
  - Scroll reveal animations
  - Animated Announcement Bar pause-on-focus
/* End: Custom Sections JS */
{% endcomment %}
<script src="{{ 'custom-sections.js' | asset_url }}" defer></script>

{% comment %}
/* Start: Mega Menu Enhancement */
  Renders Koelleza-style mega menu CSS + JS:
  - Hover-triggered dropdowns (desktop)
  - Mobile accordion behavior
  - Keyboard navigation (Tab + Enter + Escape)
  - Soleil yellow accent underlines
/* End: Mega Menu Enhancement */
{% endcomment %}
{%- render 'mega-menu' -%}

{% comment %} /* End Soleil + Custom Sections Stylesheets */ {% endcomment %}
{% comment %} Aquí puedes agregar nueva información al código sin romperlo {% endcomment %}
